          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1663689979267-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the sauce is thickening, chop your<strong> basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Once thickened, remove from heat and stir in <strong>half </strong>of your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>(save the rest for garnish!) until melted</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
